column4: NSLOCTEXT("[81E6852245F2A898B5F05E84EDC1DC2E]", "088CB3F1456A60DF983640A33040CC28", "Shell Newspaper Eigth {LineBreak}Alien Digimon appears: We have found the UFO. The creature showed its body and spoke unknown words. Is the creature an Alien? Will it appear again?")

NSLOCTEXT("[81E6852245F2A898B5F05E84EDC1DC2E]", "69C03FB147D6E2EC136371BF28E3DF50", "Shell Newspaper Seven {LineBreak}Myotismon denies his retirement: In an interview, he denied the rumors. He is still working hard. He loves his fans. He also announced that his pupil, SkullGreymon, will make his debut.")

NSLOCTEXT("[81E6852245F2A898B5F05E84EDC1DC2E]", "0ABF2908471FA0DCB2742298C69971A2", "Shell Newspaper Six {LineBreak}Myotismon to retire?: Rumor is that popular and able Myotismon will retire. No one at the arena has seen him. His career is at its end. He is too old.")

NSLOCTEXT("[81E6852245F2A898B5F05E84EDC1DC2E]", "557B9FAD4C137004E0F1A69226CECBBB", "Shell Newspaper Five {LineBreak}Hidden Treasure: A cool shop in Gear Savanna. This shop is only open from first to fifteenth each year. The shop manager is proud of his rare Items.")

NSLOCTEXT("[81E6852245F2A898B5F05E84EDC1DC2E]", "5D9EEB1D49B89A436F4B3482C1644F7B", "Shell Newspaper Four {LineBreak}A Legendary Digimon?: Rumor is that there is a cold weather Digimon in Freezeland. Mr. M was saved by this monster. It looked like a big snowball. Digimon who are not use to the cold, be careful!")

NSLOCTEXT("[81E6852245F2A898B5F05E84EDC1DC2E]", "0C2D74C84CB0637E37F16A8BCAF35D11", "Shell Newspaper Three {LineBreak}A Guardian for the Lake?: Lake Guardian is at Dragon Eye Lake. The Digimon-like creature was called by someone. Can this Guardian make wishes come true?")

NSLOCTEXT("[81E6852245F2A898B5F05E84EDC1DC2E]", "9E5987B646B916AF90AB53B6D59E0271", "Shell Newspaper Two {LineBreak}A UFO!: A report says the UFO is near Mt. Panorama. The UFO looks like a silver dish with light coming from the bottom. Is it an alien? More information to come.")

NSLOCTEXT("[81E6852245F2A898B5F05E84EDC1DC2E]", "176040E6425A60146BD196BDB736E556", "Shell Newspaper One {LineBreak}Bandits are gone!: {Player} found the hide out, led by Ogremon. However, Ogremon is loose and people are still worried.")
